  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Beau Rivage is the ideal hotel if you want to get out and explore Lake Maggiore and all of the walking it has to offer. Being near to the ferry departure point, it has great access to other parts of the lake too. </p>
<h2>Ideal location</h2>
<p>The hotel's next to a few trendy bars and restaurants where you can enjoy an aperitivo by the lake. These are fantastic places to relax after a long day of walking and exploring and if you're lucky you may catch a nearby bar on a jazz night! If you want a day chilling out in the sun, the hotel has an outdoor pool which is perfect for cooling down after a sun-bathing session. You can even take a stroll around the exotic gardens.</p>
<h2>Home away from home</h2>
<p>If you're looking for a family friendly, family run hotel with stunning views of the Borromean islands, then the Hotel Beau Rivage is a great choice. With its down to earth service and comfortable décor, you'll feel right at home here. We look forward to seeing you there!</p>]]></description>
