  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Garden View Rooms </strong>sleep two people and have a balcony with a garden view. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep two people and have a lake view. </p>
<p><strong>Comfort Side Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people and have a small balcony with a partial view of the lake. </p>
<p><strong>Comfort Lake View Rooms </strong>sleep two people and have a lake view. For these rooms a balcony may be available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Lake View Rooms for sole use </strong>are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p>Some rooms are available as triples, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Seating area</li>
<li>TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Twin beds</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Air conditioning</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available for €10 a day (payable locally)</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €2.50 a day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
